*vsound-0.6-r1 (12 Mar 2007)

  12 Mar 2007; Ryan Hill <dirtyepic@gentoo.org>
  +files/vsound-0.6-stdout.patch, -vsound-0.5.ebuild, +vsound-0.6-r1.ebuild:
  Added patch to fix --stdout option.  Thanks to Michael Higgins in Bug #117320.

  22 Feb 2007; Piotr Jaroszyński <peper@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Transition to Manifest2.

  16 Jun 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> vsound-0.6.ebuild:
  Remove gnuconfig update.

  07 Nov 2005; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> vsound-0.5.ebuild,
  vsound-0.6.ebuild:
  Don't install INSTALL or COPYING files.

  08 Apr 2005; Joseph Jezak <josejx@gentoo.org> vsound-0.6.ebuild:
  Marked ~ppc for bug #88231.

  03 Sep 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> vsound-0.6.ebuild:
  Stable amd64, sparc, x86.

*vsound-0.6 (25 Jul 2004)

  25 Jul 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> +vsound-0.6.ebuild:
  Version bump.  Closes bug #57873.

  19 Jul 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> vsound-0.5.ebuild:
  Added to ~amd64 and ~sparc

  20 Apr 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> vsound-0.5.ebuild:
  Added IUSE.

  12 Apr 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> vsound-0.5.ebuild:
  Fixed mirror:/// to mirror:// in SRC_URI to fix bug #47490.

  01 Apr 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> vsound-0.5.ebuild:
  nomirror.  Removed explicit S=

  26 Feb 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  vsound-0.5.ebuild:
  Removing realplayer from DEPEND.  Closes bug #41387.

